# Docker Based WebAPP Runtime

## Installing

### Requirements:

- Vagrant

### Config:

Edit `Vagrantfile`, change mapped host port and number of web server instances.

### Startup:

Execute `vagrant up` in the root dir of this project.

After everything is ready, you will be able to access the webapp from `http://127.0.0.1:8080`

## Deployment

Use script 'deploy.sh' to build and commit new version of code

## Scaling

Use script 'scale.sh <number of instance>' to change number of instances of app.

